
=======
Changes
=======


0.4.0 (*2019-08-14*)
====================

- Support signaling the `uptodate` status via color: [green=up-to-date, red=run, grey=ignore, brown=Not tested], using `--uptodate_status` or `-s` option.


0.3.0 (*2019-08-11*)
====================

- Support drawing tasks in left-to-right layout using `--horizontal` or `-h` option


0.2.0 (*2019-07-27*)
====================

- Support drawing tasks in execution order using `--reverse` option


0.1.1 (*2018-07-10*)
====================

- improve description given by `doit help graph`
- print name of generated file


0.1.0 (*2018-07-07*)
====================

- initial release
